{"tid":127563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死3隻]地盤升降機急墜　3名工人慘死","createTime":"2017-02-20T07:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T09:50:46.000Z","uid":32407,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f26561eca99d00dda8ed8898f5fd48b42569804","tid":127563,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/bkncn-20170219165023139-0219_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170219%2Fbkncn-20170219165023139-0219_05011_001.html&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=580c6212\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/bkncn-20170219165023139-0219_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/photo/bkncn-20170219165023139-0219_05011_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170219%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170219165023139-0219_05011_001_02b.jpg&h=41689405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事地盤升降機從高處墜下後嚴重變形。<br />\n<br />\n內地升降機事故頻生，河南信陽市息縣一幢在建樓盤的地盤升降機（籠𨋢），今日上午9時許突然從高處急墜而下，導致升降機內三名工人死亡。息縣安全生產監督管理局工作人員表示，目前部分事故責任人已被扣查，事故原因正在調查。<br />\n<br />\n事發樓盤位於息縣人民醫院附近，共有14層。現場一名男子表示，三名死者均為男性，息縣本地人；其中一人是他的叔叔，年約40歲，另外兩名死者50多歲。據其提供的照片顯示，事發現場拉有警戒線，一部地盤升降機疑從高處墜下後，嚴重變形。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f7f9ee2a986cb25627bc5dab554ffad7097c5d","tid":127563,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914eec9ccaf8b9704baaa09aad22413f37ab85e2","tid":127563,"uid":39572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641d376ec7c9e5ef4de4